# GitHub Packages registry configuration for @elevanaltd scope
# Registry redirect: @elevanaltd packages come from GitHub Packages, not public npm
@elevanaltd:registry=https://npm.pkg.github.com/

# Authentication:
# - Local Dev: Uses global ~/.npmrc (hardcoded token)
# - GitHub CI: Uses setup-node action (automatic NODE_AUTH_TOKEN)
# - Vercel: Uses environment variable (configured in dashboard)
#
# Note: The _authToken line is NOT included in this repo-level .npmrc
# to avoid conflicts. Local dev relies on global ~/.npmrc configuration.
